{"tid":1535643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[親身經歷]海港城黑心師奶炒義士之韓系店長","createTime":"2019-09-03T12:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T17:16:02.000Z","uid":317342,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c0355b12b700b2e1a6d1f3cc3ebf658f7ecb739e","tid":1535643,"uid":317342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"上次見到有巴打出咗個po話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">海港城3樓某韓系品牌炒咗義士</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1462989/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1462989/page/1</a><br />\n睇到之後我同幾個朋友都分別去過幾次，諗住睇下佢係咪咁西啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢d都係我地嘅親身經歷，個感覺真係唔太好<br />\n早幾日仲得一個sales喺度serve客，咁大個場得一個人又真係幾厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次去參觀嘅時候見到有個呀姐係<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色頸帶</span>，其他人都係<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色</span><br />\n咁我就諗呢個呀姐唔通就係主角－－<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑心店長</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢真係一啲 image都無架喎，間舖賣少女feel嘅嘢佢著到成個師奶咁<br />\n啲公仔著啲衫又唔好睇，娘味濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要個場次次都係亂嘅，地下總有幾件衫<br />\n<br />\n同佢接觸咗幾次，無花無假真係西<br />\n叫咗佢幾次都唔理我地，完全無視客人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問佢件衫放邊又叫我<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己睇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講真係以為我地得罪咗佢呀<br />\n對啲sales又惡，有個sales行開咗掛衫，佢見唔到個sales就大大聲話佢唔見咗人<br />\n最重要嘅係，有次揀緊衫嘅時候<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽到佢照啲 sales肺</span></span>！就係照緊上次巴打個po！<br />\n朋友仲有話聽到佢話佢住嗰區有示威<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻住佢搞到佢返唔到屋企呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢句我就唔在場，巴絲自己判斷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再唔係就自己去感受下 真係好西"},{"pid":"84cbdeb1c9fd7a89f69ee24c189052cc17157c53","tid":1535643,"uid":202540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:22:36.000Z","msg":"又係佢啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a873c0cbd4a2904fd0b7204bae925d5a2e172c","tid":1535643,"uid":317342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:22:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推推推</span></span>"},{"pid":"4ef47cf9498600afd56c53a38cb3e8bd1b3dbca1","tid":1535643,"uid":257980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17446b3b77519d128df064bf413510135fa964c","tid":1535643,"uid":202540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0355b12b700b2e1a6d1f3cc3ebf658f7ecb739e","tid":1535643,"uid":317342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"上次見到有巴打出咗個po話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">海港城3樓某韓系品牌炒咗義士</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1462989/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1462989/page/1</a><br />\n睇到之後我同幾個朋友都分別去過幾次，諗住睇下佢係咪咁西啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢d都係我地嘅親身經歷，個感覺真係唔太好<br />\n早幾日仲得一個sales喺度serve客，咁大個場得一個人又真係幾厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次去參觀嘅時候見到有個呀姐係<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色頸帶</span>，其他人都係<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色</span><br />\n咁我就諗呢個呀姐唔通就係主角－－<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑心店長</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢真係一啲 image都無架喎，間舖賣少女feel嘅嘢佢著到成個師奶咁<br />\n啲公仔著啲衫又唔好睇，娘味濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要個場次次都係亂嘅，地下總有幾件衫<br />\n<br